HEADWORD: Caoutchin
<hw>Caout"chin</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Chem.)</fld>
<def>An inflammable, volatile, oily, liquid hydrocarbon, obtained by the
destructive distillation of caoutchouc.</def>⟦br⟧
